<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><a name="OLE_LINK2"></a><a name="OLE_LINK1"><span style="mso-bookmark: OLE_LINK2;"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>Е С Л И<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Х О Ч Е Ш Ь<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Б Ы Т Ь<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>С Ч А С Т Л И В Ы М&hellip;<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></a></p>
